                     <hi rend="largeCaps">MARTHA DAWSON</hi> (32)</persName> was indicted<rs id="t18580104-187-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18580104-187-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18580104-187-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp> for a like offence.</rs>
